snippet.title: The Eminence in Shadow: Master of Garden Global Launch Trailer (iOS/Android)
snippet.description:
Download the new anime RPG and instantly earn massive rewards at https://got.cr/eis_announce_yt!

Not the main character, not the last boss. The one who lurks in the shadows. 

The latest anime RPG coming to iOS, Android, and soon after to PC based on the new hit anime, "The Eminence in Shadow," is now available for pre-registration!

Follow The Eminence in Shadow: Master of Garden on social!
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/emishadow.rpg
Twitter: https://twitter.com/emishadow_rpg
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/emishadow_rpg/?hl=en

#TheEminenceinShadow #MasterofGarden #emi_rpg
